SQL_STMT_U.val: select DocEntry, ObjType,docStatus,canceled,FinncPriod from ogji WITH (NOLOCK) where (DocDate between ':1' and ':2') and canceled <> 'C' :3 order by docentry desc

ExpSyntax.val: MlsTrans('Which One Do You Want To Print? (YES for header, NO for detail)')

SQL_STMT_U.val: select row_number() OVER (ORDER BY T0.DocEntry desc) as 'No' ,T0.CardName as 'Distributor' ,T0.NumAtCard as 'No.TRO' ,T0.DocNum as 'No.Faktur' ,T0.DocDate as 'Tgl.Faktur' ,T0.DocTotal as 'Nilai Faktur' ,T0.DocTotal-T0.PaidToDate as 'Dibayar Sisa Tagihan' ,T0.DocStatus as 'Status' ,T0.BaseType as 'Base Type' ,T0.ObjType as 'Object Type' from OPCH T0 where (T0.CardName like '%'+ISNULL(':2','')+'%') and (T0.DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (T0.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and CONVERT(Nvarchar(15), T0.DocNum) like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' :6 and (T0.DocType = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') and T0.canceled <> 'C' and (T0.canceled = ':8' or ':8' is null or ':8' = '') :9 :10 :11 order by T0.docentry desc

SQL_STMT_U.val: select T0.DocDate as 'Posting Date' , T0.DocNum as 'Document Number' , T0.CardName as 'Supplier Name' , TRIM(REPLACE(T0.numatcard,char(59),' ')) as 'Supplier Reference' , T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT as 'Consignee' , T0.DocCur as 'Currency' , T0.AuthCode as 'BL Number' , T1.Dscription as 'Item Name' , T1.U_IDU_QtyPack as 'Qty Pack' , T1.U_IDU_UOMPack as 'UOM Pack' , T1.Quantity as 'Qty' , T1.unitMsr as 'UOM Qty' , T1.Price as 'Price' , T1.LineTotal as 'SubTotal' ,T1.Vatsum as 'Total PPn' , T0.doctotal as 'Total' ,T0.PaidToDate as 'Total Paid' ,T0.DocTotal - T0.PaidToDate as 'Balance Due' ,Trim(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(T0.comments,char(13),' '),char(10),' '),Char(59),' ')) as 'Remarks' , T0.DocStatus as 'Status' ,T1.basetype as 'Base Document' ,T1.baseref as 'Base Number' ,T0.ObjType as 'Object Type' from OPCH T0 join PCH1 T1 on T0.DocEntry=T1.DocEntry where (T0.CardName like '%'+ISNULL(':2','')+'%') and (T0.DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (T0.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and CONVERT(Nvarchar(15), T0.DocNum) like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' :6 and (T0.DocType = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') and T0.canceled <> 'C' and (T0.canceled = ':8' or ':8' is null or ':8' = '') :9 :10 :11 order by T0.docentry desc
